  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PRIME PROTOCOL</strong>™</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prime Protocol is a high-stakes extraction platformer built around commitment, consequence, and choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/6f98908313989cdbd618516ffc21d52d.avif?t=1773888065\" width=1560 height=827 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Artifacts and Units are found and carried during run.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/d547be77421236e9a2b3058682dde180.poster.avif?t=1773888065\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/d547be77421236e9a2b3058682dde180.webm?t=1773888065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/d547be77421236e9a2b3058682dde180.mp4?t=1773888065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Only what you extract is kept. Die carrying it, and it’s gone.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/b4ee07a63cf44e45afac9d5d16a4175a.poster.avif?t=1773888065\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/b4ee07a63cf44e45afac9d5d16a4175a.webm?t=1773888065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/b4ee07a63cf44e45afac9d5d16a4175a.mp4?t=1773888065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take on the Daily Run and <u>MAX</u> Instability and push for a higher place on the Daily leaderboard.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/3010d32ddb52dbc1037192c45b11369d.poster.avif?t=1773888065\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/3010d32ddb52dbc1037192c45b11369d.webm?t=1773888065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/3010d32ddb52dbc1037192c45b11369d.mp4?t=1773888065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Early Access Roadmap</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prime Protocol will continue evolving through Early Access. The roadmap below reflects current development direction and may change over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4278160/extras/0c45ecabe1c436c76d2679187f1466bf.avif?t=1773888065\" width=1560 height=2192 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SUPPORT / FOLLOW DEVELOPMENT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prime Protocol is actively evolving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >support development</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >participate early</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >follow updates</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >observe the protocol as it grows</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >visit the official website for updates, public records, and live system status.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prime Protocol™</strong> and <strong>Prime Operator™</strong> are trademarks of Prime Protocol Interactive LLC.</p>",
